data.description: Sellers are motivated!!  Assumable mortgage at 2.375%.  Home warranty included. Welcome to this beautifully updated 3 bed/2 bath home! Located in a gated community, this property boasts fresh paint applied to the exterior and interior. The landscaping has been updated including the Rainbird irrigation system, enhancing the curb appeal of the property. The heart of this home is its remodeled kitchen, featuring all new appliances, elegant quartz countertops and a sleek hood vent. All ceiling fans have been replaced, and all light fixtures have been updated to create an inviting atmosphere. Amenities include a resort style pool, which includes a lap pool for those sunny days, as well as bocce and pickleball courts for some friendly competition. Tennis enthusiasts will appreciate the tennis courts, and for those who enjoy staying fit, there's a well-equipped fitness center. Plus, a community room provides a great space for gatherings and events.    This property offers it all. Don't miss the opportunity to make this updated and amenity-based home your own. It's a perfect blend of modern living and community convenience. Come and experience the best of what this property has to offer!
